text:
Personnally, I had a lot of hopes about this movie, I hoped really hard that they hid Tron, the character, from us by not showing him like Kevin Flynn in the trailers and that he would do a little appearance at the end, especially since we know that he probably survived at the end of Legacy and also changed side to become a good guy again, but no, he wasn't here at all. I was sooooo sad about that ;-;
Even Sam Flynn and Quora, we just see them one time as a photo like in newspaper or something, that's really a miss oportunity.

But on the other end, I was extremely surprised to see once again the arena from the 1st Tron, with the same hole in the wall, the old lightcycle, and also Flynn's arcade with the basement, that was nice, but that's all ^^'
